{"id": "1452214379411144755", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "The A2 Chapter 4 major enemies have Tentacles that keep growing in number the more time it passes, and most times they interact directly with them.\nWhat I think, and what others have expressed, is that it seems like too much of a dps check and constant damage source, that is also very disruptive for DR and it doesn't interact with counter.\nNormally the fights have some scaling mechanics, like staking str\\madness\\etc, but the tentacle gathering ramp up too fast, and most enemies have intentions that further boost the tentacle damage on top of that.\nOnly Murphy have a mechanics that lower the tentacle numbers if you can damage her enough, and even there, is normally not enough because the incredible fortress and non decaying shields she get.\n\nI think this mechanic should be looked in more an possibly tone down or reworked in some other way. \n**What do you think?**", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T08:21:28.890000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-21T09:27:31.408000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}, {"emoji": "IMG_20251113_181453", "emoji_id": "1448240235757568133", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1452214380140695675", "filename": "UI_Summon_D_Icon_Career2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 20605, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452214379411144755/1452214380140695675/UI_Summon_D_Icon_Career2.png?ex=69cc2cc9&is=69cadb49&hm=2be87704cb0df29dbc3e680b58d20112111bbb5f2865112a5dadd067b8d47848&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452215362232914004", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1226191881877061725", "author_name": "twilightsparkle163163", "author_bot": false, "content": "This top-2 bad mechanic after poison for unblocked dmg mechanic", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T08:25:23.213000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452215373310197781", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "595414429957619725", "author_name": "dracozion", "author_bot": false, "content": "I also agree, the past 2 tides W5 bosses Murphy and Gmurphy essentially are checks of if you can kill the boss before turn 6. The tentacles mechanic heavily punishes stall and any team comp that is not just burst. It is especially frusturating when many of the bosses in the tide have the mechanic and there is no way to remove tentacles/weakness and str reduction is largely ineffective against them.", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T08:25:25.854000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452215893995159652", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1226191881877061725", "author_name": "twilightsparkle163163", "author_bot": false, "content": "On alert 5 gathering is just extra 1000 dmg in ur face(+already 1k+ attacks)", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T08:27:29.995000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452216200666026136", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "Another thing, i notice that they are starting to use the Corrosion effect on enemies a lot now, probably to encourage consistent dps rather than complete one-shots, and so enemies have more hp to compensate.\nThen why put an anti dps mechanic when most enemies use this feature?", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T08:28:43.111000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-21T08:29:38.463000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
