{"id": "1452231228341227683", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "It would be better if the go up only during particular intentions, starting a lot weaker", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T09:28:25.988000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-21T09:28:45.659000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452238296611553280", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "330867601691639809", "author_name": "rain_scarlet", "author_bot": false, "content": "i agree the mechanics seems really strong on enemy, most team cant survive Gmurphy's 6th (or was it 7th) turn that is a multi-hit hitting for 1K + 1K, though it could be just Gmurphy? other enemy with this mechanics at least feels manageable on the tentacle damage front", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T09:56:31.195000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-21T09:56:38.236000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452239098650562620", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 19, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "And Murphy? mostly for the increased survivability and the fact that she double them with an intention", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T09:59:42.416000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["330867601691639809"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1452238296611553280", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452239398505807953", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "337981494641295360", "author_name": "omenatyyppi", "author_bot": false, "content": "I think all these tentacle enemies are simply very unfun to fight", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T10:00:53.907000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452239691746115617", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "Still, it need to be analyzed, at least in the more problematic cases.\nSome chap 4 enemies have the intention that limit your damage by 35% until you are above 50% hp, is pretty hard to be consistently above 50% when you take ramping passive damage every turn", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T10:02:03.821000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452240533245399041", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "Plus, as i said, different enemies are using the Corrosion effect at turn start to encourage sustained dps, and probably they have an inflated hp pool because of that, but how can you try to help people to do consistent damage and at the same time give a constantly ramping passive damage every turn that force you do at least try to go defensive even during non offensive intentions?", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T10:05:24.450000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-21T10:10:12.867000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452360060192952361", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "595414429957619725", "author_name": "dracozion", "author_bot": false, "content": "Other issue is that it essentially nullifies barrier and DR", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T18:00:21.895000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452373651335942145", "channel_id": "1452214379411144755", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "yeah, salvador rouse is a non factor in all those enemy, or tawil special effect", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T18:54:22.276000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452214379411144755", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tentacle Gathering for Enemies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1452341946680082472", "channel_id": "1452341946680082472", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "命輪「命運賭輪盤」在一般關卡和相位對弈都有內建計數器和比例顯示，好希望其他有次數上限與比例差異的命輪和密契也能得到計數器或顯示器。另外也希望有冷卻時間的裝備也能獲得類似不死鳥的復活冷卻的倒數計時器。\n\n我目前以手邊物資及商店看得到的資料整理出了有次數上限、冷卻會合及比例效果的裝備，這份整理可能有缺漏，僅供參考：\n\n>> 一次：\n溯洄時計、跨越疼痛、\n虔誠的偉力、珊瑚女之死、於暴雨之中、\n沉入殷紅、\n被縛的歌謠、迷失的道路、\n迫近的太陽、\n靈魂誕生（各一次）、\n盒中童趣（整趟探索）、聖火中的指引（整趟探索）\n塔薇狂氣爆發、\n「24」超限爆發、波呂克斯超限爆發\n\n>> 兩次：\n隱密的誕生、\n女王的戒律、快樂魔法秀、\n記憶症候\n\n>> 三次：\n星天之獸、堅韌意志、\n蒼白後裔、\n聚首時刻、苦咒縛、切割與傷害、\n猩紅之擁、\n索蕾爾超限爆發\n\n>> 三回合冷卻：\n安息之吻、\n不可承受的自由、\n你我終將重逢、\n甜蜜蛞蝓\n\n>> 五次：\n隱世的輪轉、永恆安魂曲、\n重生於湮土、\n銀鱈魚的決心（兩回合共用）、\n奧瑞塔超限爆發、卡茜亞超限爆發、\n薩爾瓦多超限爆發（整趟探索）\n\n>> 按比例：\n無垢啟示錄、光合祭禮、\n吞噬產生的護盾和臨時力量\n\n>> 死亡抵抗次數換算比例：\n克珀珊特狂氣爆發、\n菲茵特啟靈三\n\n>> 其他換算：\n墨菲技能卡「螺湮逆流」", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T16:48:23.297000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-24T11:28:33.644000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}], "attachments": [{"id": "1452341947288125520", "filename": "IMG_1343.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 133509, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452341946680082472/1452341947288125520/IMG_1343.png?ex=69cbfad7&is=69caa957&hm=c123ce7ca8efd0ed946896a8f97e957aeb4249f8699c27946fc8f68a694b5709&"}, {"id": "1452341947774533775", "filename": "IMG_1888.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 84624, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452341946680082472/1452341947774533775/IMG_1888.png?ex=69cbfad7&is=69caa957&hm=6edba6c50c6aad6ced09d38c88962ee27cdd0592a5d4684bf88fb30537536058&"}, {"id": "1452341948206809341", "filename": "IMG_1892.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 60827, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452341946680082472/1452341948206809341/IMG_1892.png?ex=69cbfad7&is=69caa957&hm=8aecef28c354522b1a1578d986fc8087ecfbfd75d4fb6e20e7a0e80117cfbbf3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452341946680082472", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」可否增設命輪和密契的計數器", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
