{"id": "1452226281708982385", "channel_id": "1452053913791627437", "type": 19, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "let's hope that it will get fixed with the patch tomorrow.\nIt seems that if you use any VPN, in different regions, it may work", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T09:08:46.619000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["105316637493706752"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1452225127587774535", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452053913791627437", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Error 502", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1452218034608406610", "channel_id": "1452218034608406610", "type": 0, "author_id": "140102992035577856", "author_name": "pyros_", "author_bot": false, "content": "When cards have too much text on them, scrolling becomes weird. Specifically, the start of the scrolling will be based on where you click on the card itself, rather than simply starting from the top. \n\nThis isn't an issue for most cards, but for very long ones it is.\n\nAn easy example is Hyperflare. When holding Hyperflare, if you don't click near the top of the card, you will be unable to see the damage value on it (because it's in the first line). If you move the card around a bunch it can sometimes appear briefly but the only way to read it properly is to click on top of the card (and read before it scrolls down). You cannot scroll back up with the mouse wheel either.\n\nAnother example is most of the special story mode cards once they're fully upgraded. For example chapter 6 card or arc2 chapter 3 card (including the unique card you get during the last boss).\n\nA potentially \"easy\" fix would be to make it so it always starts from the top regardless of where you click on the card to hold it. Alternative allow scrolling back up with mousewheel(might not be very useable on mobile though).\n\nAdded a video of the issue with Hyperflare.\nhttps://youtu.be/9hFKzfZBlPM", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T08:36:00.357000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "Morimens long description bug", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9hFKzfZBlPM", "description": "Bug report"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452218034608406610", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Scrolling issues on cards with long descriptions", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1452337512868479087", "channel_id": "1452337512868479087", "type": 0, "author_id": "1001696859225591869", "author_name": "o5214658", "author_bot": false, "content": "1,先說確實的錯字部分：生“發”的，應該是由於簡體字轉繁體字所造成的錯誤。\n\n2,開頭描述上說是奶油“蛋糕”小塊，但在後續的所有描述都是餅乾體，且味道上也不存在蛋糕部分。\n可能開頭描述的用詞改成奶油“點心”小塊之類的會比較好？\n或者變成在該開頭描述句最前面加個“看起來像是”或“看著似乎是”之類的主觀描述，來避免與後面的客觀描述事實產生衝突？", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T16:30:46.194000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452337513414000691", "filename": "Screenshot_20251222-0016412.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 442147, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452337512868479087/1452337513414000691/Screenshot_20251222-0016412.jpg?ex=69cbf6b6&is=69caa536&hm=ab852fb2bcc1774772c8e55d79f7f6427d226090d8c9e56efb762149c0329c81&"}, {"id": "1452337513787162714", "filename": "Screenshot_20251222-0016022.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 275356, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452337512868479087/1452337513787162714/Screenshot_20251222-0016022.jpg?ex=69cbf6b6&is=69caa536&hm=8f86bbdfb49c7b5c90d26b894f4a56849f8cf81948b98fefa66d5d6dec8b9658&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452337512868479087", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」繁中，杜勒賽因繁衍狂熱劇情錯字與描述疑惑。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1452340596256805056", "channel_id": "1452337512868479087", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "盲猜，可能蛋糕指的是點心整體，餅乾是指蛋糕下面硬的底部，像是水果塔那樣的？或者蛋糕指的是🍰裡黃色的部分奶油是白色，櫻桃相對於emoji裡草莓的位置，然後在蛋糕底部額外有一層硬底，可以拿取（上面的部分太軟無法拿取）。硬底是餅乾，因此餅乾實際被描述為餅乾「的部分」，餅乾只是蛋糕的一部分而已。", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T16:43:01.331000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452337512868479087", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」繁中，杜勒賽因繁衍狂熱劇情錯字與描述疑惑。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1452427103499718716", "channel_id": "1452337512868479087", "type": 19, "author_id": "1001696859225591869", "author_name": "o5214658", "author_bot": false, "content": "主要是後面的描述詞完全沒有關於蛋糕的部分；櫻桃的酸甜、奶油的潤滑、餅乾的油香，都有了描述，作為主體蛋糕無味無質？這有些不合理。", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T22:26:46.265000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-21T22:26:55.130000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["259018461458595850"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1452340596256805056", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452337512868479087", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」繁中，杜勒賽因繁衍狂熱劇情錯字與描述疑惑。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
